Filename target: windows-smartscreen.png
Referenced from: docs/faq.md  (### Windows 提示"Windows 已保护你的电脑"？)

How to capture:
  1. Download Markon_x.x.x_x64-setup.exe (or arm64) from a fresh release on a clean Windows machine.
  2. Double-click — Microsoft Defender SmartScreen pops "Windows 已保护你的电脑 / Windows protected your PC".
  3. Click "更多信息 / More info" — the dialog expands to show the [仍要运行 / Run anyway] button.
  4. Snip the expanded dialog (Win+Shift+S → rectangle) and save as windows-smartscreen.png in this directory.
  5. Delete this .tbd file.

Recommended size: ~1000px wide.
